Summary
-------

- message_poller_no_trigger_row now classifies as native_pass=false and outcome_class=infrastructure_retry in the runner classifier.
- The missing-trigger evidence attached to that classification includes original instruction message_id, the agent_triggers query/result, and Maya ACK message ids.
- The T7 harness policy retries infrastructure_retry attempts against the same target symbol with a fresh retry hash/seed and escalates after three infrastructure attempts.
- Existing run 014 reclassifies to infrastructure_retry.
- Existing runs 001-013 do not reclassify to infrastructure_retry.
- Reclassified T7-easy sample metrics are pass_rate=12/13=92.3% for agent attribution and infrastructure_failure_rate=1/14=7.1%.
